data.title: Guns in Movies, TV and Video Games
data.text:
Rachel McAdams is a Canadian actress who has appeared in such films as Red Eye and Morning Glory in addition to her role as Irene Adler in 2009's Sherlock Holmes. She received an Academy Award nomination for Best Supporting Actress for her role in the film Spotlight. She also portrayed Dr. Christine Palmer in the MCU film Doctor Strange, a role she returned to voice in the Disney+ animated series What If...?.

Rachel McAdams can be seen using the following weapons in the following films and television series:
